title: Should I Move Out of My Parents’ House? (Hour 3)
description:
Dr. John Delony & George Kamel discuss:

When it makes sense to buy a second vehicle,

Preparing to move out of your parents' house,

What to do when retirement plans change,

Counting HSA contributions toward baby step 4,

Why credit cards aren't smart.


Have a question for the show? Call 888-825-5225 Weekdays from 2-5pm ET
